|               |                                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                                                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([c_custkey@0], 32), input_partitions=32                                                                                                                   |
|               |                                                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(32), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                      |
|               |                                                         CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                                                           BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                                                             MongoDBExec projection=[c_custkey, c_nationkey] filters=[{}]                                                                                                                         |
|               |                                                   CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                                                     RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([o_custkey@0], 32), input_partitions=32                                                                                                                   |
|               |                                                       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                                                         FilterExec: o_orderdate@1 >= 1994-01-01 AND o_orderdate@1 < 1995-01-01, projection=[o_custkey@0, o_orderkey@2]                                                                           |
